        1
        ≤
        i
        <
        j
        ≤
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle 1\leq i<j\leq n}
  . In particular, if V is a Vandermonde matrix, then 
  
    
      
        
          ∏
          
            i
            <
            j
          
        
